    <lb n="1"/>Σαραπάμμων Πιπερᾶτι. 

    <lb n="2"/>ἔπεμψά σοι ἐπιστολὴν διὰ τοῦ ἀρτο-

    <lb n="3"/>κόπου καὶ <choice><corr>ἴσως</corr><sic>εισως</sic></choice> οἶδας τί σοι ἔγραψα. 

    <lb n="4"/>καὶ εἰ μὲν <choice><corr>ἐπιμένεις</corr><sic>επιμενις</sic></choice> σου τῇ ἀπονοί-

    <lb n="5"/>ᾳ, <choice><corr>συγχαίρω</corr><sic>συνχερω</sic></choice> σοι· εἰ δὲ μετανοεῖς σὺ οἶ-

    <lb n="6"/>δας. ἴσθι δὲ ὅτι <choice><corr>ὀφείλεις</corr><sic>οφιλις</sic></choice> φόρους καὶ ἀπο-


    <lb n="7"/>φορὰς ἑπτὰ <num value="7"/> ἐτῶν, ὡς <choice><corr>ἐὰ<supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">ν</supplied></corr><sic>ε<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear></sic></choice> μὴ ἀποκα-

    <lb n="8"/>τασ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear>ασίας <app type="BL"><lem resp="1.428"><sic><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">μ</supplied>ὴ</sic></lem><rdg><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">δ</supplied>ὴ</rdg></app> πέμψῃς <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ο</supplied>ἶδάς σου τὸ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ν</supplied> 

    <lb n="9"/>κίνδυνον. </ab></div><div n="meta.31368" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.31368" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="300" notBefore="276" type="textDate">spätes III</date></p></div><div n="meta.31368" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Rückseite: P.Tebt. II  335. Auf derselben Seite: P.Tebt. II  404.</p></div><div n="meta.31368" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Tebt.</title><biblScope type="volume">2</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">424</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">31368</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="DDbDP"><series>0206</series>; <biblScope type="volume">2</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">424</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0206;2;424" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.31368" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl default="NO" type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">XI</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">279</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.31368" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.31368" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikationen</head><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" subtype="other" type="publication">Sel. Pap. I 154</bibl><bibl default="NO" subtype="other" type="publication">Tibiletti, Lettere private 17</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.31368"